{
  "stem": "24884.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It upset me a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went out of Berlin and-- to his house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as we drove out, the first American soldiers entered the city.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was-- that was the moment I can never, never, never forget and describe to anybody.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We had made it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The feeling?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, we are liberated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we saw the Americans coming in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They came in from the west while the Russians came from the east.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had to go out to the west, to the house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that guy must have thought I'm a nut, because I ran over to them, and I hugged them and I kissed them and I screamed.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I cried.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we realized that we were saved.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] That feeling, you cannot describe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You can't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't think anybody could.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was a housewife in Glienicke after the war was over.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, I lived quite comfortable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My husband got me  a housekeeper.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And after we found my mother, and the baby, and we were all united, we had quite a comfortable life.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we had very nice American and British friends.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had a neighbor of my husband who we knew as a little boy who came back with the English army as a soldier.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And through them, we met a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were invited to American parties and to British parties.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had a very nice life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We came to this country in '47.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In March of '47.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I didn't-- I-- I couldn't look at the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
